  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nOn Prater genesis with our extremely overloaded beacon seems to process block 2 (late) from somewhere (db, gossip?) and when processing it's attestations throws `ATTESTATION_ERROR_PAST_EPOCH` 178 times (all of them + some other block? note MAX_ATTESTATIONS=128). Is this error expected?\r\n\r\n```\r\n2021-03-23 15:18:42 [CHAIN]         verbose: Clock slot slot=93\r\n2021-03-23 15:18:42 [CHAIN]           debug: Block pools:  pendingBlocks=0, currentSlot=93\r\n2021-03-23 15:18:42 [CHAIN]         verbose: Block processed slot=2, root=0x629bd2acd1af7e70c0bc8a53bf28a6c3ca869106c23a4217c5bb03cdd8292690\r\n2021-03-23 15:18:42 [CHAIN]         verbose: New chain head headSlot=2, headRoot=0x629bd2acd1af7e70c0bc8a53bf28a6c3ca869106c23a4217c5bb03cdd8292690\r\n...\r\n2021-03-23 15:18:42 [CHAIN]           debug: Attestation error code=ATTESTATION_ERROR_PAST_EPOCH, attestationEpoch=0, currentEpoch=2\r\nError: ATTESTATION_ERROR_PAST_EPOCH\r\n    at validateAttestation (/root/lodestar/packages/lodestar/src/chain/attestation/validate.ts:39:11)\r\n    at processAttestationJob (/root/lodestar/packages/lodestar/src/chain/attestation/processor.ts:44:5)\r\n    at AttestationProcessor.processAttestationJob (/root/lodestar/packages/lodestar/src/chain/attestation/processor.ts:28:11)\r\n    at fn (/root/lodestar/packages/lodestar/src/chain/eventHandlers.ts:238:42)\r\n    at CompositeListTreeHandler.readOnlyMap (/root/lodestar/node_modules/@chainsafe/ssz/src/backings/tree/array.ts:347:19)\r\n    at readOnlyMap (/root/lodestar/node_modules/@chainsafe/ssz/src/backings/readOnlyIterate.ts:25:43)\r\n    at BeaconChain.onBlock (/root/lodestar/packages/lodestar/src/chain/eventHandlers.ts:237:10)\r\n    at ChainEventEmitter.<anonymous> (/root/lodestar/packages/lodestar/src/chain/eventHandlers.ts:37:7)\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
